    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/fabf72c48d20a01c299fba66540afefe.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>2X25 年。经过技术飞跃和处理器的进化，人工智能能够欺骗人类并控制核武器。从那时起，人们就被迫服从人工智能。是谁击落了飞船？Cybrids 是谁？为什么这个星球被列为无生命星球？当地居民为什么如此具有攻击性？主角究竟为什么在这里？所有这些事件都不是偶然的<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/861b57f8b9b75fbf62b7f682f3ecafc8.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>Flashloop 是一款 2D 冒险游戏，带有 3D 图形，游戏发生在一个庞大而相互关联的世界中。您扮演 Cybrid，并试图在坠机后找到散落在该地区的飞船零件。突然间，这个星球变得比乍一看要可怕得多。丛林、荒地、沼泽、雪原、烧焦的土地——探访所有地方，寻找船长可能还没有准备好的答案……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/65affe59d18b1c9db9c6c0be86ccc346.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>游戏特色<br>-这是一款经典的 Metroidvania，而不是 Rouglike<br>-这里没有程序生成，整个世界都是手动组装的。一切都经过仔细测试，以获得游戏体验和感觉<br>-周到的关卡设计。最小回溯。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/8339cd7e308eb6bd426116d96df1854f.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>- 反应灵敏的 360° 控制，没有任何惯性<br>- 完全控制地面和空中的角色<br>- 您可以向前奔跑并向后射击<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/cc2dd4ef936ca74e788d1ece2dd6483c.poster.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/cc2dd4ef936ca74e788d1ece2dd6483c.webm?t=1763127912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/cc2dd4ef936ca74e788d1ece2dd6483c.mp4?t=1763127912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>- 升级您的武器，获得能力和装备，解决谜题并发现秘密，与怪物和 Boss 战斗 - 所有这些都将帮助您发现新区域并推进故事。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/f16f6d97785c92da6332825611832659.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>-«难学 - 易精通»。乍一看，敌人似乎很难对付，但通过了解敌人的行为，您可以在不受到伤害的情况下击败他们。<br>- 游戏的成功取决于玩家的技能，而不是游戏的随机性。<br>- 引人注目的视觉风格。可怕星球的自然科幻背景<br>- 所有屏幕截图和游戏画面均直接从游戏中捕获，没有任何色彩校正或滤镜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/658101d726c07480208b474db2f1f697.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>- 孤独的氛围。没有拟人化的生物。<br>- 专有音乐。真正让您沉浸在氛围中<br>- 游戏由戏剧导演独立开发。<br>- 周到的游戏玩法。游戏一步一步构建，戏剧性十足，吸引着玩家的兴趣<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/822fbbf51a31f10fa9728fb691094eb5.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 /></span><br>- 游戏有一把电磁炮。这种武器非常有趣。尤其是当你击中目标时<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/816315a865fd67b3de77eb7e989a0371.poster.avif?t=1763127912\" width=630 height=142 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/816315a865fd67b3de77eb7e989a0371.webm?t=1763127912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3069130/extras/816315a865fd67b3de77eb7e989a0371.mp4?t=1763127912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
